MEMORY MAP:


ADDRESS				DESCRIPTION

0000-03FF			AVG PCB PROGRAM RAM
0800 INPUTS			D0=RIGHT COIN SW
				D1=CENTER COIN SW
				D2=LEFT COIN SW
				D3=SLAM SW
				D4=SELF TEST SW
				D5=DIAG STEP SW
				D6=VG HALT
				D7=3 KHZ

0A00 & 0C00			OPTIONS

				AVG PCB:
1000 OUTPUTS			D0=COIN COUNTER RIGHT
				D1=COIN COUNTER CENTER
				D2=COIN COUNTER LEFT

1200				VG GO
1400				WATCHDOG
1600				VG RESET

1800				READS D7 MATH STATUS (1=BUSY, 0=DRIVE)
1802				READS D7 FIRE SWITCH (0=OFF, 1=ON)
1802				READS D6 START SWITCH (1=OFF, 0=ON)
1804				READS D7-D0 MATH RESULT-LOW BYTE
1806				READS D7-D0 MATH RESULT-HIGH BYTE

1808				WRITES D7-D4 CRASH AMPLITUDE (0=OFF, F=LOUDEST)
				D3 START LED (1=OFF, 0=ON)
				D2 SHOT SOUND (0=OFF, 1=ON)
				D1 SQUEAL SOUND (0=OFF, 1=ON)
				D0 POT SELECT
180A				WRITES X NOISE RESET
180C				WRITES D3-D0 EAROM CONTROL

1810-181F			READ/WRITE D7-D0 POKEY
1820-185F			D7-D0 EAROM

1860-187F			WRITE D7-D0 MATH BOX INPUTS

2000-2FFF (4K)			VECTOR RAM
3000-3FFF (4K)			VECTOR ROM

4800-7FFF (14K)			PROGRAM ROM
